OL,3,CCommunity providing 'TLC' for those in
OL,4,Cneed
OL,6,FCommunities in Cumbria are swapping
OL,7,FEaster Eggs for essentials in their
OL,8,Fdonations to food banks amid rising
OL,9,Fcosts for poverty-stricken families.
OL,11,FHethersgill's festival committee have
OL,12,Fstarted an Easter campaign to provide
OL,13,FTLC (toiletries, larder items and
OL,14,Fcleaning products) for the Brampton
OL,15,FFood Bank to distribute among the
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,18,FDonations are being collected and
OL,19,Fsorted at the Black Lion pub in
OL,20,FHethersgill.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
