CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773241885
OL,3,CCommunity providing 'TLC' for those in
OL,4,Cneed
OL,6,FMarti Irving, who runs the pub said:
OL,7,F"When you look at your own shopping
OL,8,Ftrolley, there's the food, which is an
OL,9,Fessential. But the pricey items are
OL,10,Fcleaning items and toiletries.
OL,12,F"And that's why it was important for
OL,13,Fus not to just say, oh, let's get some
OL,14,FEaster eggs for the food bank for
OL,15,FEaster, which sounds, on the surface,
OL,16,Fa really good idea.
OL,18,F"But when we asked them, they said,
OL,19,Fwell, actually it would be better if
OL,20,Fyou did this."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
