OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773241885
OL,3,CCommunity providing 'TLC' for those in
OL,4,Cneed
OL,6,FThe food bank supplies weekly food
OL,7,Fpackages to more than fifty families
OL,8,Fin the area north of Carlisle.
OL,10,FThe organisers told ITV Border that
OL,11,Fthey are thousands of pounds short of
OL,12,Fwhat they need to supply users with
OL,13,Fadequate cleaning products and
OL,14,Ftoiletries.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
